[{"id":"RAW_89e8effa","title":"GLM-5 技术报告：技术细节全公开","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzI3NzQ0Mg==&mid=2247493485&idx=1&sn=bc8337e1e3095c4a29f20dd46161a14a","date":"2026-02-22 09:40:00","oneSentenceSummary":"智谱发布下一代基础模型 GLM-5，通过 DSA 稀疏注意力、异步强化学习基础设施及智能体算法创新，推动 AI 从“氛围编程”向“智能体工程”跨越。","summary":"本报告详述了 GLM-5 的技术架构与训练突破。GLM-5 采用 744B 参数的 MoE 架构，核心创新在于引入 DeepSeek 稀疏注意力（DSA）以极低成本实现 200K 长上下文处理。在后训练阶段，智谱构建了全新的异步强化学习（RL）基础设施，通过解耦生成与训练过程，解决了长程智能体任务中的计算气泡问题。此外，模型针对真实软件工程场景进行了深度优化，提出了异步 Agent RL 算法及 TITO 机制，显著提升了模型在复杂、长周期交互中的自主决策与纠错能力。报告还展示了 GLM-5 在国产算力生态上的深度适配成果，以及在 ARC 基准测试和真实世界工程评估（CC-Bench-V2）中的 SOTA 表现。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_89e8effa.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"智谱","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":98,"score":93},{"id":"RAW_a567ffcf","title":"LinkedIn CEO：让你的职业生涯免受 AI 影响的 5 项技能丨 Silicon Valley Girl","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzcxMDA5NTI0OA==&mid=2247485092&idx=1&sn=c49342a6825d33d062ac8a4da75454e5","date":"2026-02-21 14:16:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_a567ffcf.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"晚点再听LaterCast","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":15,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_639978fa","title":"开发者们最近推荐了这 3 个好用的 App","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU4Mjg3MDAyMQ==&mid=2247607344&idx=1&sn=d5a3d11b71e922b35b4f291861a4eeec","date":"2026-02-21 04:11:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_639978fa.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"少数派","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":21,"score":83},{"id":"RAW_6b60a0ad","title":"硅谷巨头争抢“故事讲述者”，有人年薪超 500 万","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjc1NjM3MjY2MA==&mid=2691565061&idx=1&sn=7b2f27b047088d313fb25374c4529a02","date":"2026-02-21 03:55:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_6b60a0ad.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"腾讯科技","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":18,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_70bf8b7","title":"Build Hou